nodes.text: Anastasia Heonis is an American Greek model also known as "Acid PopTart." An illustration of the character Ailyn Vel (daughter of Boba Fett) was based on Anastasia. The artwork (by Joe Corroney) appeared in Star Wars Insider 80. An illustration of a very minor character called Thrynka Padaunete was also based on Anastasia. This artwork appeared in Star Wars Insider 71. Anastasia, both a model and artist in her own right, is a frequent collaborator with other artists, most frequently Laura Dark, Aaron Kennison and Eric Tragedy.
